<h2 class="bold font-l">"Your party has drowned"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Apparently, the operators in Washington are used to this trope. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Murdered In A Phone Booth</span>, <span>Murdered On The Phone</span> </h3>
</div>
